'''Mark Dodson''' ([[February 1]], [[1960s|1960]] &ndash; [[March 2]], [[2024]])<ref name="Death" /> was an American actor who voiced [[Salacious B. Crumb|Salacious Crumb]] in [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']], and provided various voices for ''[[Ewoks: The Battle for Endor]]'' and [[Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens|''Star Wars'': Episode VII ''The Force Awakens'']]. He is best known as the voice of the eponymous creatures in [[Wikipedia:Gremlins|''Gremlins'']] and [[Wikipedia:Gremlins 2: The New Batch|''Gremlins 2: The New Batch'']].

